# Mongo-Eco
## Every Method is structured the same! <method>(options)


# METHODS

```
//Import package
const economy = require("@shinchanop/mongo-eco");
//create new economy() Class
const eco = new economy('YOUR MONGODB URI');
```

### SetWeekly(GuildID,Amt) =>
GuildID - Guild ID for the guild  
Amt - Amount to set for weekly bonus

> Returns: {   
  gid: GuildID,    
  shopItems: Array of items in shop,   
  weeklyAmt: Amount to given weekly,   
  dailyAmt: Amount to given daily  
} 



```
//Import package
const economy = require("@shinchanop/mongo-eco");
//create new economy() Class
const eco = new economy('YOUR MONGODB URI');


eco.SetWeekly(GuildID,Amt).then(data => {
      //<Channel>.send(`WEEKLY AMT HAS BEEN CHANGED TO ${data.weeklyAmt}`)
})
```

