### Transfer(GuildID, User1ID, User2ID, Amt) => 
GuildID - Guild ID for the guild you want to remove the item
User1 - User Sending The Money            
User2 - Reciever      
Amt: Amount To Transfer   

> Returns "NOT_ENOUGH_CASH" If the first user does not have enough cash


```
//Import package
const economy = require("@shinchanop/mongo-eco");
//create new economy() Class
const eco = new economy('YOUR MONGODB URI');


eco.Transfer(GuildID, User1ID, User2ID, Amt).then(data => {
      //<Channel>.send(`${data.Amt} Has Been Transfered From User1 to User2`)
})
```

